snippet.title: Kate Moss Talks To Megyn Kelly About Modeling And Motherhood | Megyn Kelly TODAY
snippet.description:
The iconic supermodel Kate Moss, who is now the creative director of Japanese skincare company Decorte, opens up in an exclusive interview with Megyn Kelly about a wide range of topics, including how she was discovered at a young age, the importance of her privacy and being a mother. She also weighs in on how the modeling industry has changed, saying it was “freer” when she was coming up.
